description:
The Water Extraction and Liquefaction subsystem is divided into the water extraction components and the water capturing and liquefaction components. A depiction of the system can be found in Figure 1-1.  
  The water extraction components (green dashed outline) are positioned inside the thermal vacuum chamber and are connected to several interfaces on the vacuum chamber walls. The water capturing and liquefaction components (blue dashed outline) are partially inside and outside of the thermal vacuum chamber and are located downstream of the water extraction components.  
  The following chapters document the actual procured hardware components of both the Water Extraction and Liquefaction subsystems. &nbsp;

